</div></div></div>
<div class="cnn_stryspcvbx"><div class="cnn_stryspcvbxcntr"><div class="cnn_stryscbx1">
<div><a href="/2014/04/27/us/donald-sterling-lawsuits/index.html?iid=article_sidebar">Sterling has history of fighting discrimination claims</a></div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx2">
updated 6:36 PM EDT, Mon April 28, 2014
</div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx3">
<a href="/2014/04/27/us/donald-sterling-lawsuits/index.html?iid=article_sidebar"><img src="http://i2.cdn.turner.com/cnn/dam/assets/140427155221-sterling-stiviano-file-video-tease.jpg" alt="" border="0" height="68" width="120"/></a>
</div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx4">Los Angeles Clippers owner Donald Sterling is a billionaire real estate mogul who's owned the team for more than three decades.</div>
<div class="cnn_clear"></div>
</div></div></div>
<div class="cnn_stryspcvbx"><div class="cnn_stryspcvbxcntr"><div class="cnn_stryscbx1">
<div><a href="/2014/05/14/us/donald-sterling-interview/index.html?iid=article_sidebar">Donald Sterling: I'm not a racist, I'm a giver</a></div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx2">
updated 9:12 AM EDT, Thu May 15, 2014
</div>
<div class="cnn_stryscbx3">
